  "content": "<div><i><tt><br></tt></i></div>\n<div><i><tt>---</tt></i></div>\n<div><i><tt><br></tt></i></div>\n<div><i><tt>### I. | GOAL</tt></i></div>\n<div><i><tt><br></tt></i></div>\n<div><i><tt>To ensure all outputs from this system are usable on-the-go, every module will be exported in a format that works seamlessly in iPhone Notes (and optionally Notion or GitHub).</tt></i></div>\n<div><i><tt><br></tt></i></div>\n<div><i><tt>---</tt></i></div>\n<div><i><tt><br></tt></i></div>\n<div><i><tt>### II. | EXPORT FORMAT STRUCTURE</tt></i></div>\n<div><i><tt><br></tt></i></div>\n<div><i><tt>Each module includes:</tt></i></div>\n<div><i><tt><br></tt></i></div>\n<div><i><tt>- </tt></i><b><tt>**Header**</tt></b><i><tt> (e.g., `::GR1ND3R [PROJECT PROFILE]`)</tt></i></div>\n<div><i><tt>- </tt></i><b><tt>**Context Framing**</tt></b><i><tt> (short summary, placement in system)</tt></i></div>\n<div><i><tt>- </tt></i><b><tt>**Main Content**</tt></b><i><tt> (tagged, editable, with subheadings)</tt></i></div>\n<div><i><tt>- </tt></i><b><tt>**Next Steps / Metadata**</tt></b><i><tt> (integration options, status, REF_</tt></i><tt>ID)</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>---</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>### III. | EXAMPLE MODULE STRUCTURE</tt></div>",
